sources.title: Enemies Among Us | Full Movie | Action Drama | Billy Zane
sources.description:
Enemies Among Us - It's not politics as usual, or is it? The governor of Louisiana is about to become the vice-presidential candidate for his party but a murder and an international web spanning from South Africa to Pakistan and North Korea might just get in the way.
2010.  Stars: Billy Zane, James DuMont, Eric Roberts, Robin Givens
